formula.name: Single KPI
formula.text: SUM(CASE WHEN KPI("Prediction") = 'delayed' THEN KPI("NETWR_CONVERTED") ELSE 0.0 END)

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( "PY_DDP_PREDICTIONS"."Y_PRED" ) = 1 THEN 'no prediction' WHEN "PY_DDP_PREDICTIONS"."Y_PRED" > 0.5 THEN 'delayed' ELSE 'not_delayed' END AS "Prediction"

variables.name: filter8
variables.value:
CASE WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."LOEKZ") = 1 THEN 'not deleted'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'S' THEN 'locked'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'
     ELSE "EKPO"."LOEKZ"
END
